eventContent: You will be retired in 10 years. Time really flies!
At the age of 60, what do you think of your retirement life? Which kind are you yearning for?
Congratulations on your retirement!Ready to  live an ideal life?
You have been retiring for five years, and time would never ever waiting for you...

You thought you would have a healthy life, but unfortunately when you was 80 years old...
85 is the age of having a grandson! Wait, my wife! Old companion? Wife...
